1
00:00:07,970 --> 00:00:13,095
Lolo Roman, thank you
so much for guiding us.

2
00:00:13,779 --> 00:00:17,239
And now, we're about to
have another grand reopening.

3
00:00:17,978 --> 00:00:20,105
Thank you so much, and we love you.

4
00:00:20,938 --> 00:00:21,940
Yes.

5
00:00:22,723 --> 00:00:26,270
Mom, you really can’t
forget Lolo Roman, can you?

6
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,446
Of course, Andres!

7
00:00:28,471 --> 00:00:34,305
Even though he’s not here, Lolo Roman
should definitely be part of this occasion.

8
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:39,548
Besides, if it weren’t for his hard
work, we wouldn’t even have this bakery.

9
00:00:40,407 --> 00:00:44,108
That’s true. And it’d be
risky if we didn’t do this.

10
00:00:44,228 --> 00:00:44,983
Yeah.

11
00:00:45,008 --> 00:00:49,012
If you didn’t invite Lolo Roman,
he might just crash this event!

12
00:00:49,378 --> 00:00:49,791
Right!

13
00:00:49,816 --> 00:00:52,367
- What do you mean gate crash?
- It’s not impossible!

14
00:00:52,675 --> 00:00:54,476
- I’m serious!
- Like, as a spirit? Crash the event?

15
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:54,974
Yes!

16
00:00:55,034 --> 00:00:59,370
Remember the creepy stuff that
happened here in Barangay Singko before?

17
00:00:59,395 --> 00:00:59,935
What, what, what?

18
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:01,961
It could happen again, right?!

19
00:01:03,449 --> 00:01:04,996
- Wait a minute…
- Hmm?

20
00:01:05,021 --> 00:01:07,781
Let’s not talk about things
like that; it might come true!

21
00:01:07,822 --> 00:01:08,769
Right?!

22
00:01:08,794 --> 00:01:10,368
Let’s not scare each other.

23
00:01:10,393 --> 00:01:13,638
You never know; a
spirit might show up later.

24
00:01:14,866 --> 00:01:18,556
Stop it. Come on, let’s focus.
Let’s go, let’s go, let’s go.

25
00:01:18,581 --> 00:01:19,581
Let’s go.

26
00:01:21,077 --> 00:01:21,764
What’s that?!

27
00:01:21,816 --> 00:01:24,034
Kuya Richard! You’re scaring us!

28
00:01:24,059 --> 00:01:24,781
- Andres!
- Chard!

29
00:01:24,806 --> 00:01:26,516
Relax! This is normal!

30
00:01:26,541 --> 00:01:29,000
It’s the trend now, Korean skincare…

31
00:01:29,025 --> 00:01:29,667
What’s that?!

32
00:01:29,692 --> 00:01:30,165
Huh?!

33
00:01:30,190 --> 00:01:32,312
It’s my routine! I do this every day!

34
00:01:32,337 --> 00:01:32,840
Every day—?!

35
00:01:32,865 --> 00:01:34,725
Looks very oppa-like, huh?

36
00:01:34,750 --> 00:01:37,612
Oppa-like? I’ll deal with
you, I’m warning you!

37
00:01:37,917 --> 00:01:39,310
Stop that!

38
00:02:40,256 --> 00:02:43,069
Who’s that?
That’s mine…why is there so much?

39
00:02:43,798 --> 00:02:46,558
What’s wrong with you, are
you drunk? I’m into this stuff!

40
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,739
Why so much?

41
00:02:47,912 --> 00:02:49,605
Even application!

42
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,758
Go, Boss Beauty!

43
00:02:50,783 --> 00:02:51,513
A little at a time!

44
00:02:51,538 --> 00:02:52,955
- Don’t overdo it!
- You’ve got this!

45
00:02:52,979 --> 00:02:54,124
Iskineport is just there!

46
00:02:54,694 --> 00:02:57,195
- I’m already full just looking at this!
- You’ve got this, Boss Beauty!

47
00:02:57,219 --> 00:02:59,298
- Boss Beauty!
- Represent!

48
00:02:59,323 --> 00:03:00,063
Come on, drink up!

49
00:03:00,088 --> 00:03:01,171
There you go!

50
00:03:01,411 --> 00:03:02,241
See?!

51
00:03:02,266 --> 00:03:03,266
Look at you!

52
00:03:03,291 --> 00:03:04,119
Whoo!

53
00:03:04,144 --> 00:03:05,889
- Bottoms up!
- Let's take half the shot!

54
00:03:05,914 --> 00:03:07,465
- Your turn, Chard!
- Chard! Chard!

55
00:03:07,490 --> 00:03:08,470
Kuya Aga!

56
00:03:08,495 --> 00:03:09,182
Kuya Aga!

57
00:03:09,207 --> 00:03:10,207
Kuya Aga!

58
00:03:10,297 --> 00:03:13,137
- Come join us for a drink! Come on!
- Come on!

59
00:03:13,198 --> 00:03:13,958
Kuya Aga!

60
00:03:13,983 --> 00:03:14,691
- Kuya Aga!
- No thanks.

61
00:03:14,716 --> 00:03:15,935
Join us for a toast!

62
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,139
- Thank you, thank you, thank you!
- Why?!

63
00:03:17,163 --> 00:03:21,290
I’m just here because my love told me to
light a candle since it’s All Souls’ Day.

64
00:03:21,571 --> 00:03:23,765
You know, just in case someone visits us.

65
00:03:23,993 --> 00:03:25,780
So, here. Go on!

66
00:03:25,850 --> 00:03:30,913
Kuya Aga, don’t believe
in those superstitions!

67
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,939
It’s 2024!

68
00:03:33,997 --> 00:03:37,491
Hey, but those ghost stories are true!

69
00:03:37,516 --> 00:03:43,123
If you didn’t know, there’s a
white lady on this very street!

70
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,583
Hey, that’s not true!

71
00:03:44,613 --> 00:03:46,126
You believe in that stuff?!

72
00:03:46,379 --> 00:03:47,433
Hi!

73
00:03:47,673 --> 00:03:48,673
Huh?

74
00:03:52,205 --> 00:03:53,225
White lady?

75
00:03:53,698 --> 00:03:56,211
Why is she wearing white?

76
00:03:56,612 --> 00:03:59,225
No, maybe she’s just
attending a graduation?

77
00:03:59,278 --> 00:04:01,671
Ah, that’s true!

78
00:04:02,493 --> 00:04:03,199
Back to drinking!

79
00:04:03,485 --> 00:04:04,452
Come on!

80
00:04:04,477 --> 00:04:04,959
Your turn!

81
00:04:04,984 --> 00:04:05,984
Skim some off the top!

82
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,640
- Okay, okay!
- Hey!

83
00:04:07,665 --> 00:04:08,107
Hey!

84
00:04:08,132 --> 00:04:09,500
- What’s that?!
- Almost there…

85
00:04:10,114 --> 00:04:11,148
Hey!

86
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,000
Iskineport!

87
00:04:13,272 --> 00:04:15,052
- All good?
- All good, all good.

88
00:04:15,593 --> 00:04:16,966
All good, I skimmed some off!

89
00:04:18,152 --> 00:04:20,772
But those white ladies,
they wear regular clothes.

90
00:04:20,797 --> 00:04:25,379
But the one I saw was a foreigner,
because that white lady was really pale!

91
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,205
Pretty?

92
00:04:26,352 --> 00:04:28,891
Beautiful! Glad you brought that up!

93
00:04:28,935 --> 00:04:30,869
You’re crazy. You’re crazy.

94
00:04:30,894 --> 00:04:31,948
But honestly, it’s legit.

95
00:04:32,103 --> 00:04:35,370
There’s supposedly an angel
visiting, performing miracles.

96
00:04:36,084 --> 00:04:36,704
Seriously?

97
00:04:36,729 --> 00:04:38,178
- Miracles?
- Yes, miracles!

98
00:04:38,538 --> 00:04:39,718
Oh, wait a minute!

99
00:04:40,125 --> 00:04:43,238
If that’s what we’re talking
about, you don’t have to look far.

100
00:04:43,333 --> 00:04:47,487
Here in our place, really, someone visits!

101
00:04:47,705 --> 00:04:52,802
Sometimes you’ll feel it, like
a creepy, unexplainable chill!

102
00:04:52,834 --> 00:04:54,329
- Really?
- Yes!

103
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,839
But guys, you know what?

104
00:04:56,988 --> 00:05:01,201
- They say, the more you talk about them…
- Hmm?

105
00:05:01,743 --> 00:05:04,917
- …the more likely they’ll show up.
- What?!

106
00:05:05,425 --> 00:05:09,986
That’s the scariest part. That’s
why I’m nervous about this stuff!

107
00:05:11,185 --> 00:05:12,185
Kuya!

108
00:05:12,772 --> 00:05:15,945
You’ve been hugging
Beau—ah, Mariposa, all this time!

109
00:05:16,873 --> 00:05:18,913
- What, Boss Beauty?
- Got something to say?

110
00:05:22,864 --> 00:05:24,184
- Oh!
- Did you vape?!

111
00:05:24,209 --> 00:05:25,215
Oh, Tso K!

112
00:05:25,637 --> 00:05:26,663
Boss Beauty!

113
00:05:27,272 --> 00:05:28,638
Iskineport! Chard!

114
00:05:28,663 --> 00:05:29,495
Kuya Aga!

115
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,840
- Goms!
- Where did you come from?

116
00:05:30,962 --> 00:05:31,822
Goms! It’s Goms!

117
00:05:31,847 --> 00:05:34,937
I came from a baptism! I was a godfather!

118
00:05:35,023 --> 00:05:35,402
Baptism?

119
00:05:35,427 --> 00:05:37,356
But I had a little drink.

120
00:05:37,524 --> 00:05:39,550
- That’s little?
- Uh, excuse me.

121
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:40,937
Make him drink!

122
00:05:41,017 --> 00:05:41,637
Goms!

123
00:05:41,674 --> 00:05:43,467
Baptism? Looks more like a funeral wake!

124
00:05:43,984 --> 00:05:45,764
And why doesn’t he have screws on his neck?

125
00:05:45,789 --> 00:05:46,955
Isn’t that Frankenstein?

126
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:48,228
That’s not Frankenstein!

127
00:05:48,334 --> 00:05:50,575
- That’s Frankenstein’s monster!
- You know, I’m starting to feel weird.

128
00:05:50,599 --> 00:05:51,614
- I’ll head out now, okay?
- Oh, okay, bye!

129
00:05:51,638 --> 00:05:52,507
You’re getting on my nerves!

130
00:05:52,532 --> 00:05:52,951
Yes!

131
00:05:52,976 --> 00:05:54,216
You’re starting to get annoyed!

132
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:59,909
- Bye, Kuya Aga!
- Actually, guys, I’m getting sleepy too.

133
00:05:59,934 --> 00:06:00,289
You too?!

134
00:06:00,314 --> 00:06:01,514
How do you feel sleepy?
How do you feel sleepy?

135
00:06:01,538 --> 00:06:02,538
So fast!

136
00:06:02,790 --> 00:06:05,430
Like that!
Bye, bye, bye, bye, bye, bye, bye!

137
00:06:05,603 --> 00:06:07,483
- We’re the only ones left here, huh?
- Bye-bye!

138
00:06:08,408 --> 00:06:10,802
You’re all so nosy! Gosh!

139
00:06:10,827 --> 00:06:12,399
Spirit of the glass!

140
00:06:12,492 --> 00:06:13,509
Oh, sure, why not?

141
00:06:13,534 --> 00:06:14,534
- Is that okay?
- Okay!

142
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:17,210
Let’s see if we can talk to the spirits!

143
00:06:17,235 --> 00:06:17,828
Alright, do it!

144
00:06:17,853 --> 00:06:19,908
- Just use a glass…
- Do you know how?

145
00:06:19,954 --> 00:06:20,521
Uh…

146
00:06:20,869 --> 00:06:22,549
- Do you know how?
- Let’s use this glass!

147
00:06:22,917 --> 00:06:23,464
Oh, sure…

148
00:06:23,489 --> 00:06:25,297
It just has something in it;
let me drink it.

149
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:26,917
Oh, no, don’t! You might get drunk.

150
00:06:26,942 --> 00:06:29,251
- Being drunk is bad…
- That’s true, don’t get drunk!

151
00:06:29,276 --> 00:06:29,968
If you’re calling spirits.

152
00:06:29,993 --> 00:06:31,118
- Let’s just throw it away.
- Alright.

153
00:06:31,142 --> 00:06:32,142
Ouch!

154
00:06:32,417 --> 00:06:33,450
Where’d you throw it?

155
00:06:33,475 --> 00:06:35,155
- There’s someone there!
- There’s someone!

156
00:06:35,223 --> 00:06:37,940
No, no! Let’s continue, Iskineport!

157
00:06:37,965 --> 00:06:38,630
Sorry, sorry!

158
00:06:38,655 --> 00:06:40,990
- I’ve got something ready!
- Our paper…

159
00:06:41,032 --> 00:06:42,365
- Here it is!
- What we prepared?

160
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:43,543
Here it is, this one.

161
00:06:44,007 --> 00:06:45,314
I smell like alcohol now!

162
00:06:46,284 --> 00:06:48,431
Here, Iskineport, wipe it here.

163
00:06:48,456 --> 00:06:49,457
This, oh!

164
00:06:49,814 --> 00:06:50,754
That’s my homework.

165
00:06:50,779 --> 00:06:52,176
See, it has numbers and letters!

166
00:06:52,201 --> 00:06:54,228
That’s our homework from last night, right?

167
00:06:54,825 --> 00:06:59,095
Why only up to P?! Just P to B.
Now we’ll add happy and sad emojis.

168
00:06:59,849 --> 00:07:01,355
Yeah, there you go.

169
00:07:01,388 --> 00:07:02,615
Then sad.

170
00:07:03,145 --> 00:07:04,239
Is that really a thing?

171
00:07:04,316 --> 00:07:10,080
Yes, to see if the spirit is happy or sad.

172
00:07:10,112 --> 00:07:11,492
- Ah…
- It has numbers too.

173
00:07:11,517 --> 00:07:12,517
That’s how it works.

174
00:07:12,652 --> 00:07:17,108
Oh, Atasha, Andres,
All Saints’ Day is coming.

175
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:20,086
When are we visiting
Lolo Roman’s grave?

176
00:07:20,847 --> 00:07:25,508
Uh, sorry, Mom, but I have
something urgent at work.

177
00:07:26,236 --> 00:07:27,236
What?

178
00:07:27,486 --> 00:07:28,246
Oh, you?

179
00:07:28,271 --> 00:07:29,863
Ah, me too, Mom.

180
00:07:29,888 --> 00:07:33,240
I’ve got extra work
because of work from home.

181
00:07:33,265 --> 00:07:34,966
You know how it is, right?

182
00:07:35,598 --> 00:07:41,559
You know, if we don’t
visit him, they might visit us!

183
00:07:44,416 --> 00:07:49,586
But…fine, I’ll adjust my
schedule for Lolo Roman.

184
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,273
Really?!

185
00:07:50,298 --> 00:07:51,298
Of course.

186
00:07:51,492 --> 00:07:54,811
- What about you?
- Alright, I’ll adjust too. It’s doable.

187
00:07:54,849 --> 00:07:56,583
- Lolo Roman will be happy.
- Anything for family.

188
00:07:56,607 --> 00:07:57,607
Aww…

189
00:08:00,025 --> 00:08:00,838
Hey!

190
00:08:00,863 --> 00:08:01,523
What’s that?!

191
00:08:01,548 --> 00:08:02,440
Wait, what was that?!

192
00:08:02,465 --> 00:08:04,418
Andres! Check it out;
there might be a thief!

193
00:08:04,443 --> 00:08:06,171
Wait, why…why me?! You go!

194
00:08:06,196 --> 00:08:07,296
Well, aren’t you a man?!

195
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:09,187
Aren’t you a strong, independent woman?!

196
00:08:09,212 --> 00:08:11,092
- You’re strong, right?!
- Ah, wait, wait, wait!

197
00:08:11,815 --> 00:08:15,008
Stop, stop! No more finger-pointing!
I’ll go check!

198
00:08:16,994 --> 00:08:17,775
Mom?!

199
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,787
You should just let me go! Not Mom!

200
00:08:21,143 --> 00:08:23,783
Oh no, oh no, oh no!

201
00:08:25,382 --> 00:08:26,989
White lady!

202
00:08:27,014 --> 00:08:28,734
Here it comes, here it
comes, here it comes!

203
00:08:30,096 --> 00:08:32,370
What white lady are you talking about?!

204
00:08:33,831 --> 00:08:34,438
It’s me!

205
00:08:34,619 --> 00:08:35,619
Lola Maxi!

206
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:36,150
Lola!

207
00:08:36,492 --> 00:08:40,075
- Oh my gosh! My heart!
- I fell out of bed!

208
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,938
I dreamt of Roman!

209
00:08:43,332 --> 00:08:46,812
But are you okay, Lola Maxi?
Because that was a loud thud!

210
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:50,140
I’m fine; I just dreamt of Roman!

211
00:08:50,293 --> 00:08:52,393
Was it a nightmare or not?

212
00:08:52,450 --> 00:08:53,983
No!

213
00:08:54,393 --> 00:08:56,607
I dreamt of Roman!

214
00:08:57,381 --> 00:08:59,361
He was doing something to me.

215
00:08:59,718 --> 00:09:05,295
The bed was creaking,
the whole room shaking.

216
00:09:05,588 --> 00:09:10,064
And my body’s all sore from how hard he is!

217
00:09:10,089 --> 00:09:14,328
Ah…Lola Maxi…um, there are kids here.

218
00:09:14,503 --> 00:09:16,476
What’s your problem?!

219
00:09:16,822 --> 00:09:21,166
Roman was just massaging
me. Hard massage!

220
00:09:21,672 --> 00:09:23,451
Just the way I like it!

221
00:09:24,062 --> 00:09:27,042
But my body aches all over!

222
00:09:28,225 --> 00:09:33,653
Oh, Roman, I really need
your massage! Roman!

223
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:37,024
When will you visit me?!

224
00:09:37,049 --> 00:09:39,365
- Is Lola okay?
- Why don’t we invite Lola?

225
00:09:39,398 --> 00:09:40,391
Ah, that’s a good idea, huh?

226
00:09:40,416 --> 00:09:46,823
Ghosts, ghosts! Ghosts, ghosts!
Where are you?!

227
00:09:47,064 --> 00:09:50,677
Ghosts, ghosts! Anybody there?

228
00:09:51,614 --> 00:09:55,187
Tso K, come on! Ghosts don’t have bodies!

229
00:09:55,307 --> 00:09:56,017
Hmm…

230
00:09:56,042 --> 00:09:58,095
Any spirit there?!

231
00:09:59,316 --> 00:10:04,326
Hmmm! That’s fake! Fake!

232
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:07,499
Hey!

233
00:10:07,524 --> 00:10:10,496
- Yes, it said yes!
- What?!

234
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,600
Did any of you move it?!

235
00:10:11,625 --> 00:10:12,648
- No!
- No!

236
00:10:12,944 --> 00:10:14,130
It went to yes!

237
00:10:14,155 --> 00:10:14,977
Ask it again.

238
00:10:15,042 --> 00:10:17,816
- Chef K, it went to yes!
- I saw it, I saw it!

239
00:10:17,841 --> 00:10:19,593
- Ask it again, ask it again!
- Come here!

240
00:10:19,618 --> 00:10:20,904
- Oh no!
- Ghost–.

241
00:10:21,523 --> 00:10:22,523
Iskineport!

242
00:10:22,778 --> 00:10:25,998
- Oh my gosh, I’m nervous!
- Don’t be nervous!

243
00:10:27,008 --> 00:10:29,821
Ghosts, ghosts! Ghosts, ghosts!
What’s your purpose?!

244
00:10:32,511 --> 00:10:34,997
Don’t press too hard! Just hover over it!

245
00:10:35,022 --> 00:10:36,844
This will take forever!

246
00:10:36,869 --> 00:10:38,962
Don’t be like that…oh, there!

247
00:10:40,175 --> 00:10:46,573
Y-O-U!

248
00:10:47,631 --> 00:10:48,631
You?!

249
00:10:48,664 --> 00:10:49,664
Us?!

250
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:50,885
- You!
- Us?!

251
00:10:50,917 --> 00:10:51,332
- You!
- Us?!

252
00:10:51,363 --> 00:10:52,165
We’re the purpose!

253
00:10:52,243 --> 00:10:52,823
You!

254
00:10:52,848 --> 00:10:53,957
- You!
- You!

255
00:10:53,982 --> 00:10:55,375
- You!
- You!

256
00:10:56,028 --> 00:10:56,450
You!

257
00:10:56,475 --> 00:10:57,502
I’m not part of this!

258
00:10:59,543 --> 00:11:00,543
Cowards!

259
00:11:00,712 --> 00:11:01,712
Chard, you’re a coward!

260
00:11:02,124 --> 00:11:02,972
Chef K, you’re a coward!

261
00:11:02,997 --> 00:11:04,786
Boss Beauty, you’re a coward!

262
00:11:05,890 --> 00:11:09,330
I’m the only brave one
here in Barangay Singko!

263
00:11:14,101 --> 00:11:15,101
Whoo!

264
00:11:15,127 --> 00:11:18,647
You’re all scaredy-cats!
You’re all useless!

265
00:11:21,245 --> 00:11:23,145
I’ll just close thi–.

266
00:11:37,587 --> 00:11:38,914
The glass moved?!

267
00:11:43,097 --> 00:11:44,557
And it’s upside down…

268
00:11:52,504 --> 00:11:57,076
It’s on the letter O now, and it moved to…

269
00:12:01,053 --> 00:12:02,606
- My love!
- Yes, my love?!

270
00:12:02,631 --> 00:12:07,147
Let’s set a date for when we’ll
visit Grandpa Roman’s grave!

271
00:12:07,172 --> 00:12:07,511
Mmhmm.

272
00:12:07,536 --> 00:12:10,942
And let’s go early so we can avoid traffic.

273
00:12:10,967 --> 00:12:12,252
Right. Of course.

274
00:12:12,277 --> 00:12:18,010
The only issue is I still
have a lot to fix at the bakery.

275
00:12:18,978 --> 00:12:23,489
But don’t worry, we’ll do it right away.
We’ll leave as early as we can.

276
00:12:23,514 --> 00:12:24,833
- Mmm, that’s right.
- Okay?

277
00:12:28,825 --> 00:12:30,025
- Hey!
- Iskineport!

278
00:12:30,389 --> 00:12:31,576
Hi, family!

279
00:12:32,453 --> 00:12:33,453
Good morning!

280
00:12:33,881 --> 00:12:35,874
Especially to you, Maxi!

281
00:12:36,454 --> 00:12:38,135
You’re even more beautiful in the morning!

282
00:12:38,863 --> 00:12:43,463
Anyway…do you have an outlet here?

283
00:12:43,991 --> 00:12:46,371
Oh, look, there is one!

284
00:12:51,993 --> 00:12:54,620
Hello, Maxi! How are you?

285
00:12:55,699 --> 00:12:56,899
Are you borrowing money again?

286
00:12:57,299 --> 00:12:58,299
No!

287
00:12:58,537 --> 00:13:03,951
There’s no need for an
excuse to notice your beauty!

288
00:13:04,268 --> 00:13:05,268
Psst, hey, Iskineport!

289
00:13:05,474 --> 00:13:07,853
What did you guys do last night?
You even played spirit of the glass!

290
00:13:07,877 --> 00:13:10,344
No! Sit down, Niño Mulach!

291
00:13:10,723 --> 00:13:12,790
Come on, sit down!

292
00:13:13,452 --> 00:13:17,050
Oh, wait, wait!
Did you really play spirit of the glass?

293
00:13:17,075 --> 00:13:19,712
That’s bad, you know!
You shouldn’t be doing that!

294
00:13:20,070 --> 00:13:21,070
Sssh!

295
00:13:21,487 --> 00:13:24,633
Hey, hey, hey! Don’t get
too close to Grandma Maxi!

296
00:13:26,170 --> 00:13:30,018
Nothing happened with the
spirit of the glass. Don’t worry.

297
00:13:34,083 --> 00:13:35,030
You know what I want…

298
00:13:35,055 --> 00:13:37,234
- Mmm?
- Don’t lose weight.

299
00:13:37,305 --> 00:13:38,033
Iskineport!

300
00:13:38,058 --> 00:13:39,411
What’s happening?

301
00:13:39,436 --> 00:13:42,116
Because what I like about Maxi
is how, you know, she’s full of life!

302
00:13:42,985 --> 00:13:45,372
Orb! Wow, Orb!

303
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:49,012
Kuya Iskineport was
acting so weird earlier,

304
00:13:49,738 --> 00:13:51,798
like he was turning into a
sugar daddy or something.

305
00:13:53,233 --> 00:13:54,100
Yeah, exactly.

306
00:13:54,246 --> 00:13:56,013
- Right?
- He didn’t seem like himself anymore.

307
00:13:56,037 --> 00:14:01,059
It was almost like…what’s that?
Like he was possessed or something!

308
00:14:01,084 --> 00:14:01,646
Possessed, right?

309
00:14:01,671 --> 00:14:04,805
Like something took over him. I don’t know.

310
00:14:04,830 --> 00:14:07,649
I feel like they really
used the spirit of the glass.

311
00:14:08,168 --> 00:14:09,368
It seems like it, doesn’t it?

312
00:14:09,623 --> 00:14:13,543
You know, Orb, Tash…now
that you mentioned it,

313
00:14:14,102 --> 00:14:18,168
I noticed something
strange about Tso K too.

314
00:14:18,235 --> 00:14:19,235
Hmm?

315
00:14:19,290 --> 00:14:21,923
He was there during the
ceremony last night, right?

316
00:14:22,358 --> 00:14:25,064
- Yeah, he was!
- But wait, Orb, how was he acting strange?

317
00:14:26,206 --> 00:14:27,359
It was like –.

318
00:14:28,356 --> 00:14:30,606
Oh! Ah!

319
00:14:30,631 --> 00:14:32,053
- Tso K!
- Tso K!

320
00:14:32,078 --> 00:14:33,219
Hello there!

321
00:14:33,244 --> 00:14:34,032
He–hello!

322
00:14:34,057 --> 00:14:36,085
Top of the morning to y’all kids!

323
00:14:36,473 --> 00:14:37,360
He’s speaking English?

324
00:14:37,385 --> 00:14:38,070
Oh, Anne…

325
00:14:38,095 --> 00:14:39,436
So, you know how to speak English?

326
00:14:39,460 --> 00:14:42,332
Do you mind if you stay a bit here?

327
00:14:43,005 --> 00:14:44,485
I’ll just go to the parlor…

328
00:14:44,933 --> 00:14:46,747
- The parlor?
- …to pamper myself.

329
00:14:48,353 --> 00:14:49,546
- Ah…
- Goodbye, kids!

330
00:14:49,571 --> 00:14:50,901
- Goodbye!
- Goodbye, darling!

331
00:14:50,926 --> 00:14:51,926
Goodbye, darlin’!

332
00:14:52,314 --> 00:14:53,961
Have a great time!

333
00:14:56,988 --> 00:14:59,154
What just happened to Tso K?

334
00:14:59,538 --> 00:15:03,601
There, go on. Miss, come
back, okay? See you around!

335
00:15:04,008 --> 00:15:05,114
Boss Beauty!

336
00:15:06,527 --> 00:15:07,100
Huh?

337
00:15:07,444 --> 00:15:08,444
Boss Beauty?!

338
00:15:08,624 --> 00:15:10,664
I’m not Boss Beauty anymore!

339
00:15:12,203 --> 00:15:14,936
I’m the chosen one!

340
00:15:15,887 --> 00:15:16,900
The feed?

341
00:15:17,228 --> 00:15:18,228
Feed?!

342
00:15:18,288 --> 00:15:19,155
The chosen one!

343
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:23,516
Oh, the chosen one! Which kind?

344
00:15:23,606 --> 00:15:26,953
The chosen one! Three hours, 250 pesos!

345
00:15:27,041 --> 00:15:29,433
Wait, I don’t understand you!

346
00:15:29,458 --> 00:15:33,602
What are you talking about,
and why is your voice like that?!

347
00:15:34,561 --> 00:15:36,927
I am the chosen one!

348
00:15:38,069 --> 00:15:45,051
Last night, an angel visited me
and blessed me with a pure heart!

349
00:15:46,851 --> 00:15:47,884
Oh, the chosen one!

350
00:15:49,414 --> 00:15:51,501
And the chosen one has a message!

351
00:15:52,223 --> 00:15:54,489
You all need to know this!

352
00:15:55,906 --> 00:15:57,199
There’s a miracle!

353
00:15:59,251 --> 00:16:00,958
Miracles are real!

354
00:16:01,466 --> 00:16:04,360
Miracles are in all our hearts!

355
00:16:04,863 --> 00:16:07,003
Miracles are in people’s hearts!

356
00:16:07,042 --> 00:16:09,849
And there’s a miracle in this store!

357
00:16:09,874 --> 00:16:11,433
Here, here, here!

358
00:16:11,883 --> 00:16:15,249
From here on out, no one will go hungry,

359
00:16:15,904 --> 00:16:17,504
and no one will turn to drugs!

360
00:16:19,117 --> 00:16:20,397
Yes, that’s right! That’s right!

361
00:16:20,721 --> 00:16:26,871
Because everyone will get
one kilo of free rice per person!

362
00:16:26,896 --> 00:16:32,564
Oh! Hey! Hey! Goms, Goms! Save
some for me! Save some for me!

363
00:16:33,136 --> 00:16:38,532
Hey, wait a minute, Boss Beauty,
won’t you go bankrupt doing this?

364
00:16:40,051 --> 00:16:41,051
Hello?

365
00:16:41,977 --> 00:16:43,117
Hello?

366
00:16:44,125 --> 00:16:44,958
Please line up!

367
00:16:44,983 --> 00:16:45,985
You’ll all get something!

368
00:16:46,219 --> 00:16:49,565
Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey! Ah! Ah!

369
00:16:50,449 --> 00:16:51,503
Anyway, here’s the next one.

370
00:16:51,527 --> 00:16:52,527
Is that the first one?

371
00:16:54,136 --> 00:16:55,623
Hello, Lola Maxi!

372
00:16:57,889 --> 00:16:58,889
Orb?

373
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:03,869
Tash, Orb, I just came from outside.

374
00:17:04,782 --> 00:17:08,961
I saw Boss Beauty giving out
rice to the entire neighborhood.

375
00:17:09,476 --> 00:17:12,762
She said she was possessed by an angel.

376
00:17:13,395 --> 00:17:17,361
Wasn’t she one of the people who
did the spirit of the glass last night?

377
00:17:18,320 --> 00:17:20,833
So, our suspicion was correct, Andres?

378
00:17:21,755 --> 00:17:24,001
Oh my god, they’re
really getting possessed!

379
00:17:24,427 --> 00:17:25,594
What are we going to do?

380
00:17:25,692 --> 00:17:29,260
As far as we know, the
ones possessed are Tso K,

381
00:17:29,284 --> 00:17:32,852
Boss Beauty, and
Kuya Iskineport, right?

382
00:17:32,877 --> 00:17:34,078
- Kuya Iskineport…
- Is that right?

383
00:17:34,102 --> 00:17:37,335
…we’re not sure yet if Kuya
Iskineport is one of them, Orb.

384
00:17:37,977 --> 00:17:39,817
That’s why we’re still observing him.

385
00:17:40,996 --> 00:17:41,996
Oh.

386
00:17:43,409 --> 00:17:44,602
Who’s that boss –.

387
00:17:51,253 --> 00:17:52,920
Maxi, take your clothes off!

388
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,000
Aray…

389
00:17:56,127 --> 00:18:00,920
Maxi, I’m not trying to disrespect you.

390
00:18:01,505 --> 00:18:04,305
What I mean is, take off your clothes

391
00:18:04,978 --> 00:18:06,971
so I can give you a massage.

392
00:18:07,612 --> 00:18:13,209
I know your body hurts because you dreamed
about me last night and fell off the bed.

393
00:18:13,234 --> 00:18:14,234
Isn’t that right?

394
00:18:14,555 --> 00:18:16,249
What are you even talking about?

395
00:18:17,592 --> 00:18:20,958
Maxi, do you still not believe me?

396
00:18:21,622 --> 00:18:23,808
Do you want me to prove it to you?

397
00:18:24,695 --> 00:18:26,668
Come on, let me massage you.

398
00:18:27,207 --> 00:18:28,207
Fine.

399
00:18:28,462 --> 00:18:34,081
If you’re really Roman, I’ll ask
you something only he would know.

400
00:18:34,321 --> 00:18:34,975
Go ahead.

401
00:18:35,062 --> 00:18:38,636
How many moles do I
have, and where are they?

402
00:18:39,647 --> 00:18:44,124
You have three moles. One on
the back of your neck, right here.

403
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:47,228
One on your waist, here.

404
00:18:48,317 --> 00:18:49,317
And one on your…

405
00:18:56,374 --> 00:19:00,800
It really is you! You’re Roman!

406
00:19:01,721 --> 00:19:03,468
Why are you crying?

407
00:19:03,701 --> 00:19:05,621
Are those tears of joy?!

408
00:19:06,887 --> 00:19:13,611
It’s just…of all the people
Roman could possess, why you?!

409
00:19:14,177 --> 00:19:17,777
- I can’t, I can’t, I can’t!
- Maxi! Maxi!

410
00:19:17,844 --> 00:19:18,904
I can’t!

411
00:19:19,716 --> 00:19:21,943
- Confirmed!
- Confirmed!

412
00:19:22,386 --> 00:19:25,473
Oh my golly! Maxi!

413
00:19:26,441 --> 00:19:28,173
- It hurts.
- Possessed!

414
00:19:30,017 --> 00:19:33,217
Why did I punch the wall of this house?!

415
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:35,250
Maxi!

416
00:19:35,405 --> 00:19:37,711
- Confirmed, confirmed. Confirmed.
- Possessed!

417
00:19:38,242 --> 00:19:39,242
My love!

418
00:19:39,438 --> 00:19:44,072
I got some rice from Boss
Beauty’s store. She’s giving it away!

419
00:19:44,604 --> 00:19:46,877
- Boss Beauty is giving away rice?
- Yes!

420
00:19:47,479 --> 00:19:49,139
What is even happening today?

421
00:19:49,164 --> 00:19:51,317
Can this day get any stranger?!

422
00:19:51,342 --> 00:19:52,582
I don’t understand any of it!

423
00:19:52,607 --> 00:19:54,746
Me neither. I don’t get it either.

424
00:19:57,998 --> 00:19:58,998
Karl?!

425
00:20:01,928 --> 00:20:02,928
Karl?!

426
00:20:03,432 --> 00:20:04,119
BFF?!

427
00:20:04,185 --> 00:20:05,552
Hello, Darling!

428
00:20:05,645 --> 00:20:06,645
Ah?

429
00:20:07,104 --> 00:20:09,851
Hey, girl! I’m not talking to you!

430
00:20:10,487 --> 00:20:12,754
I’m talking to my daddy hunk!

431
00:20:13,216 --> 00:20:14,502
What?! Hunk?!

432
00:20:15,004 --> 00:20:17,457
What’s happening to you, BFF? Tell me!

433
00:20:18,063 --> 00:20:19,063
Hmmm!

434
00:20:20,384 --> 00:20:25,199
Come closer, and I’ll whisper! Come!

435
00:20:28,253 --> 00:20:30,894
- Hey!
- Oh my gosh!

436
00:20:30,926 --> 00:20:32,328
Yummy?

437
00:20:32,353 --> 00:20:35,274
BFF! Tso K! BFF, what’s happening to you?!

438
00:20:36,695 --> 00:20:37,975
What did you guys do last night?

439
00:20:38,009 --> 00:20:38,529
What?

440
00:20:38,935 --> 00:20:42,728
- What did you do last night?
- Oh, nothing!

441
00:20:43,097 --> 00:20:46,237
We just did the spirit of the glass!

442
00:20:46,262 --> 00:20:48,179
- Spirit of the glass?!
- Spirit of the glass?!

443
00:20:48,256 --> 00:20:52,562
Oh no, my love, could it
be that he’s possessed?

444
00:20:53,724 --> 00:20:54,431
BFF?

445
00:20:54,456 --> 00:20:56,195
- Hmm?
- You’re possessed!

446
00:20:56,294 --> 00:20:58,054
- What’s possessed?
- You’re possessed!

447
00:20:58,145 --> 00:21:00,778
Admit it! You’re possessed,
BFF! You’re possessed!

448
00:21:02,774 --> 00:21:04,987
Fight it! Fight it!

449
00:21:05,067 --> 00:21:05,541
BFF!

450
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,600
Oh! You see that?!

451
00:21:06,825 --> 00:21:08,451
- That hurt, you know!
- No!

452
00:21:08,476 --> 00:21:09,943
But you need to fight it!

453
00:21:09,968 --> 00:21:10,968
Why did you slap me?!

454
00:21:11,483 --> 00:21:12,690
BFF, you’re possessed!

455
00:21:12,715 --> 00:21:14,194
- I was possessed?!
- Yes!

456
00:21:14,219 --> 00:21:15,307
You’ve turned into a woman!

457
00:21:15,332 --> 00:21:17,829
- Then what should I do, huh?!
- Fight it!

458
00:21:18,023 --> 00:21:19,803
What if I’ve been holding it in?!

459
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:22,093
It’s hard, but…

460
00:21:23,486 --> 00:21:25,759
but I just can’t fight it!

461
00:21:25,784 --> 00:21:28,020
- Oh, BFF!
- I just can’t fight it!

462
00:21:28,045 --> 00:21:30,133
- Fight it, BFF!
- I just can’t fight it!

463
00:21:30,177 --> 00:21:35,050
BFF, BFF, BFF! You can do it, fight it!

464
00:21:39,584 --> 00:21:40,584
Oh, what happened?

465
00:21:40,678 --> 00:21:43,059
- That’s what I’ve been saying!
- Why do you keep hitting me?!

466
00:21:43,083 --> 00:21:45,324
No, BFF! You’re possessed!

467
00:21:45,349 --> 00:21:47,476
- You’re possessed!
- What happened?!

468
00:21:47,565 --> 00:21:48,752
You’re turning into a woman!

469
00:21:48,777 --> 00:21:49,868
You said it yourself:
“I just can’t hide it!”

470
00:21:49,892 --> 00:21:51,275
- “And I can’t fight it!”
- Really?!

471
00:21:51,299 --> 00:21:52,540
I can’t fight it, right?!

472
00:21:52,565 --> 00:21:54,018
- It’s happening?!
- Yes!

473
00:21:54,043 --> 00:21:54,342
Yes!

474
00:21:54,367 --> 00:21:55,382
What do I do? Why is this happening?!

475
00:21:55,406 --> 00:21:57,683
I don’t know, but you need
to…there, are you okay now?

476
00:21:57,708 --> 00:21:58,777
- But, but –
- Are you okay now?

477
00:21:58,801 --> 00:21:59,463
Are you good?

478
00:21:59,587 --> 00:22:01,267
Wait…am I okay? It seems…

479
00:22:02,126 --> 00:22:02,846
seems like I’m okay.

480
00:22:02,893 --> 00:22:04,393
- I think so.
- Are you sure?

481
00:22:04,418 --> 00:22:06,705
Phew, you really scared me there!

482
00:22:06,730 --> 00:22:07,705
Yeah, same here.

483
00:22:07,730 --> 00:22:09,538
- All good?
- All good, all good!

484
00:22:09,563 --> 00:22:11,468
Harder not to be your girl!

485
00:22:11,493 --> 00:22:12,957
- Hey!
- BFF!

486
00:22:12,982 --> 00:22:14,986
- Your girl! Joy to the world!
- BFF, BFF! Wait, wait!

487
00:22:15,010 --> 00:22:16,058
Stay here, stay here!

488
00:22:16,083 --> 00:22:18,173
- My love, my love, my love!
- I don’t like you!

489
00:22:18,198 --> 00:22:20,503
- Back off! I don’t like you!
- Me?!

490
00:22:20,528 --> 00:22:22,728
- You’re the one I like!
- Wait, wait, hold on, hold on!

491
00:22:23,669 --> 00:22:24,869
Thank you, Boss Beauty.

492
00:22:26,384 --> 00:22:27,977
Thank you so much, Boss Beauty.

493
00:22:28,379 --> 00:22:29,379
Hey!

494
00:22:31,855 --> 00:22:32,855
Wow!

495
00:22:32,959 --> 00:22:35,419
Excuse me! Hello!

496
00:22:35,634 --> 00:22:37,114
Who are you looking for?

497
00:22:37,139 --> 00:22:40,271
I’m Ted Makipot!

498
00:22:40,817 --> 00:22:41,684
Ah, reserved…

499
00:22:41,709 --> 00:22:48,173
Our team flew in because we heard there’s
paranormal activity in this neighborhood.

500
00:22:48,198 --> 00:22:49,788
Team?! What team?

501
00:22:50,256 --> 00:22:52,415
Oh, oh! But yes, it’s here!

502
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:55,111
That person, that one!
She’s possessed by an angel!

503
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:58,116
An angel possessed
her, but I’m a bit skeptical.

504
00:22:58,141 --> 00:23:04,914
Look, her face is still the same,
but her behavior has changed. Right?

505
00:23:10,080 --> 00:23:11,486
Are you Ted Makipot?

506
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:14,874
Perfect, Boss Ted.

507
00:23:14,899 --> 00:23:17,044
We brought another one who’s possessed.

508
00:23:21,829 --> 00:23:23,836
What are you doing?! No, it’s not allowed!

509
00:23:24,797 --> 00:23:27,337
Stop it! Stop it!

510
00:23:28,792 --> 00:23:30,984
I don’t wanna talk to you, lady!

511
00:23:31,009 --> 00:23:33,195
No, BFF—wait!

512
00:23:34,103 --> 00:23:36,823
Boss, are you Ted Makipot?

513
00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:37,900
Ted.

514
00:23:37,966 --> 00:23:42,037
Ted Makipot, the exorcist,
the expert on paranormal stuff?

515
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:44,016
Is it you? Is it you?

516
00:23:44,041 --> 00:23:46,156
Because my BFF!

517
00:23:46,542 --> 00:23:47,522
Can you check him out?

518
00:23:47,562 --> 00:23:48,842
The vibrations are heavy!

519
00:23:48,867 --> 00:23:51,410
- There, see?
- = This, you didn’t guess it!

520
00:23:52,245 --> 00:23:54,284
- This! There’s something!
- What’s happening?

521
00:23:58,072 --> 00:23:59,072
Three are possessed.

522
00:24:00,165 --> 00:24:01,824
- Three?!
- Three?!

523
00:24:02,388 --> 00:24:03,768
Gather them in the center!

524
00:24:04,738 --> 00:24:06,698
- BFF, no!
- Please believe me!

525
00:24:06,769 --> 00:24:07,283
No, please!

526
00:24:07,308 --> 00:24:08,296
Please believe me!

527
00:24:08,321 --> 00:24:09,761
- No, no. I’m okay!
- No, you’re not!

528
00:24:11,666 --> 00:24:13,393
Just listen, please!

529
00:24:15,278 --> 00:24:17,438
There it is! There it is!

530
00:24:18,539 --> 00:24:19,539
There it is!

531
00:24:19,893 --> 00:24:22,533
Ted Makipot, I just have
one simple question.

532
00:24:22,706 --> 00:24:25,046
Can you help our friend here?

533
00:24:27,105 --> 00:24:28,372
I feel something…

534
00:24:28,612 --> 00:24:30,313
He's been feeling
something for a while now!

535
00:24:30,337 --> 00:24:32,275
Yeah! What is it? What is it?!

536
00:24:33,235 --> 00:24:33,881
for you.

537
00:24:34,255 --> 00:24:34,728
Oh.

538
00:24:34,915 --> 00:24:35,481
What?

539
00:24:35,506 --> 00:24:36,479
For you, he said!

540
00:24:36,504 --> 00:24:37,560
For me?!

541
00:24:37,927 --> 00:24:38,673
What?!

542
00:24:38,698 --> 00:24:41,384
I feel like you’re girlfriend material.

543
00:24:41,409 --> 00:24:46,042
H my god! That’s so—wait, Ted, okay?

544
00:24:46,067 --> 00:24:48,730
Let’s work first. Let’s
focus for now, okay?

545
00:24:48,755 --> 00:24:49,968
- Right!
- Later, later.

546
00:24:50,396 --> 00:24:51,396
Here we go!

547
00:24:52,586 --> 00:24:55,193
I feel like an angel…

548
00:24:55,446 --> 00:24:57,033
- An angel?
- …has possessed him.

549
00:24:57,217 --> 00:24:58,117
- An angel?!
- An angel?!

550
00:24:58,142 --> 00:25:00,087
- An angel?!
- An angel!

551
00:25:00,667 --> 00:25:03,386
- Huh? An angel?!
- Doesn't it seem like it?

552
00:25:03,559 --> 00:25:04,226
Tso K…

553
00:25:04,252 --> 00:25:08,610
He’s possessed by… a
white lady who's a foreigner!

554
00:25:10,408 --> 00:25:11,925
Whoa! Fancy!

555
00:25:12,052 --> 00:25:14,358
Classy! So classy!

556
00:25:14,528 --> 00:25:16,341
And he’s possessed by…

557
00:25:18,075 --> 00:25:18,688
What?!

558
00:25:18,713 --> 00:25:22,407
- …an old man who’s…
- What?!

559
00:25:22,782 --> 00:25:24,662
- …super…hot!
- Hot?!

560
00:25:24,687 --> 00:25:27,388
- Hot!
- You’ve really got the hots!

561
00:25:28,372 --> 00:25:29,579
Why were they possessed?

562
00:25:29,773 --> 00:25:32,606
They disrespected the day of the dead.

563
00:25:32,631 --> 00:25:35,807
- That’s what I’ve been saying, right?!
- Right? Isn't it…

564
00:25:35,832 --> 00:25:38,314
They played spirit of the glass!

565
00:25:38,339 --> 00:25:40,564
- Spirit of the glass?!
- Spirit of the glass!

566
00:25:41,074 --> 00:25:42,074
Oh, the glass!

567
00:25:42,570 --> 00:25:44,456
Wait, how do we put things back to normal?

568
00:25:45,411 --> 00:25:50,122
You need to find the glass
they used for spirit of the glass!

569
00:25:50,147 --> 00:25:52,547
The glass! We’ll get it!

570
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:55,060
They drank at our place last night.

571
00:25:55,450 --> 00:25:56,790
- Let’s go find it.
- Let’s go!

572
00:25:56,815 --> 00:25:57,747
The day of the dead?

573
00:25:57,772 --> 00:26:00,982
- Isn’t that the guy who betrayed Christ?
- Huh?

574
00:26:01,253 --> 00:26:01,793
That’s Judas!

575
00:26:01,818 --> 00:26:09,818
Excuse me, Sir Ted, but maybe you could
just return Iskineport and Tso K to normal.

576
00:26:10,040 --> 00:26:14,049
Boss Beauty became kind after
being possessed by the angel.

577
00:26:14,074 --> 00:26:15,268
- Yeah, that’s true!
- Yeah!

578
00:26:15,293 --> 00:26:20,909
Yeah, right?! So maybe
she could just stay that way!

579
00:26:21,944 --> 00:26:29,291
Honestly, that’s true.
I’m hot, but only for Maxi.

580
00:26:29,398 --> 00:26:30,378
No one else.

581
00:26:30,403 --> 00:26:33,942
- Oh, Iskineport, leave Grandma Maxi alone.
- Who’s Iskineport?

582
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:38,680
Oh, right. Lolo Roman,
leave Lola Maxi alone.

583
00:26:38,739 --> 00:26:41,533
Me too. I-I’ll behave.

584
00:26:41,665 --> 00:26:42,279
Yes.

585
00:26:42,304 --> 00:26:45,523
And at the same time,
I will be a proper wife.

586
00:26:46,179 --> 00:26:48,786
But, please, leave your ugly wife!

587
00:26:48,811 --> 00:26:51,494
Hey, what ugly wife?!

588
00:26:51,519 --> 00:26:52,120
Oh, my love…

589
00:26:52,145 --> 00:26:54,004
Get her away from
me, or I’ll pull her hair!

590
00:26:54,029 --> 00:26:57,470
My love, my love, my love,
my love, my love! My love, relax!

591
00:26:57,495 --> 00:26:59,840
What are you saying?! Stop it, or else!

592
00:26:59,865 --> 00:27:01,327
- Where’s Maxi?
- My love!

593
00:27:02,324 --> 00:27:02,858
Calm down.

594
00:27:02,883 --> 00:27:04,490
Calm down, calm down, calm down. Okay?

595
00:27:04,665 --> 00:27:05,665
Is that okay now?

596
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:12,044
Oh, my! What a day!

597
00:27:13,370 --> 00:27:17,684
I overslept! Oh, kids!

598
00:27:18,677 --> 00:27:19,250
Kuya Chard!

599
00:27:19,275 --> 00:27:20,803
What are you looking for there?

600
00:27:20,828 --> 00:27:24,647
Kuya Chard, where’s the glass you used
last night for the spirit of the reading?

601
00:27:25,257 --> 00:27:26,943
- Spirit of the reading…
- Yeah…

602
00:27:26,968 --> 00:27:29,470
- …or spirit of the glass?
- Oh, spirit of the glass!

603
00:27:29,495 --> 00:27:32,118
Spirit of the glass? Oh! I know that!

604
00:27:32,497 --> 00:27:34,990
- The clear one, super visible!
- Yes, yes!

605
00:27:35,015 --> 00:27:36,279
- Yeah, that one!
- Yeah!

606
00:27:36,304 --> 00:27:39,471
The one this big with designs?

607
00:27:39,496 --> 00:27:40,746
- Yes!
- Yeah, yeah, that one!

608
00:27:40,771 --> 00:27:44,656
The one Lola Maxi sometimes
uses to store dentures?

609
00:27:44,771 --> 00:27:46,605
- That’s the one!
- Yeah, that one!

610
00:27:47,386 --> 00:27:48,466
I have no idea where it is.

611
00:27:49,528 --> 00:27:50,528
Hat?!

612
00:27:50,585 --> 00:27:54,705
Kuya Chard, after all that,
you don’t know where it is?!

613
00:27:55,199 --> 00:27:58,679
Well, I wasn’t the one who
cleaned up last night, okay?!

614
00:27:59,331 --> 00:28:01,645
- Oh, geez!
- So where is it?

615
00:28:02,460 --> 00:28:04,006
Where’s that glass?!

616
00:28:04,299 --> 00:28:05,299
It’s not here.

617
00:28:05,705 --> 00:28:06,299
Right?

618
00:28:06,383 --> 00:28:07,823
Maybe…

619
00:28:07,848 --> 00:28:08,888
I thought he already knew.

620
00:28:09,848 --> 00:28:11,688
- - It’s in her room?
- I’m gonna have a drink!

621
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:18,793
- That’s the glass!
- That’s it!

622
00:28:19,165 --> 00:28:20,465
- Oh, my!
- This is the glass?!

623
00:28:20,776 --> 00:28:24,349
Sorry, sorry, Kuya
Chard, we’re just in a rush.

624
00:28:27,536 --> 00:28:30,003
Uh, Ted, what are you doing now?

625
00:28:30,389 --> 00:28:32,022
I’m praying over the glass.

626
00:28:33,290 --> 00:28:40,470
Now, we’ll sprinkle this on
them to remove the spirits.

627
00:28:41,230 --> 00:28:44,691
Okay. Lolo Roman, any last words?

628
00:28:45,315 --> 00:28:53,315
Uh…Aga, Cha, just visit
me at my grave, okay?

629
00:28:55,394 --> 00:28:57,408
Bring Lola Maxi with you.

630
00:28:57,614 --> 00:28:59,188
- Okay, okay.
- Okay, Lolo Roman.

631
00:28:59,213 --> 00:29:00,213
I love you.

632
00:29:00,382 --> 00:29:01,662
I love you guys, okay?

633
00:29:01,687 --> 00:29:02,155
Why…

634
00:29:02,180 --> 00:29:04,755
- We love you too!
- Why does Lolo Roman seem different?

635
00:29:05,048 --> 00:29:06,048
Here it comes!

636
00:29:10,832 --> 00:29:12,645
Dirt! So much dirt!

637
00:29:12,670 --> 00:29:14,668
What do you mean dirt?

638
00:29:17,872 --> 00:29:19,119
Oh, my! Oh, oh!

639
00:29:20,178 --> 00:29:21,238
What’s happening?!

640
00:29:31,353 --> 00:29:31,640
Oh!

641
00:29:31,773 --> 00:29:32,600
- Oh!
- Oh!

642
00:29:32,625 --> 00:29:33,501
- Oh!
- Oh!

643
00:29:33,622 --> 00:29:34,842
- What happened?
- Where am I?

644
00:29:35,048 --> 00:29:36,181
You’re back!

645
00:29:36,780 --> 00:29:38,660
What’s happening, why
are there so many people?!

646
00:29:38,685 --> 00:29:40,722
- Iskineport!
- I’m Iskineport!

647
00:29:44,804 --> 00:29:46,147
Why is everyone clapping, Kuya?

648
00:29:46,172 --> 00:29:47,531
Because, uh…

649
00:29:47,670 --> 00:29:48,710
What happened to me?!

650
00:29:48,735 --> 00:29:54,853
Kuya Iskineport, you were possessed,
and you flirted with Lola Maxi.

651
00:29:54,878 --> 00:29:56,200
I flirted with Lola Maxi?! Yuck!

652
00:29:56,321 --> 00:29:57,835
She smells like urine!

653
00:29:57,860 --> 00:29:58,828
Hey, you’re so rude!

654
00:29:58,853 --> 00:30:00,926
- That’s Lola Maxi you’re talking about!
- Oh, sorry!

655
00:30:00,950 --> 00:30:03,288
- I liked Lola Maxi?!
- Yes! A lot!

656
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:05,370
You became Lolo Roman!

657
00:30:05,395 --> 00:30:06,395
Yes!

658
00:30:06,456 --> 00:30:07,773
- Really?
- That’s enough!

659
00:30:07,798 --> 00:30:10,535
- Good thing I’m back.
- White lady.

660
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:13,090
White lady, any last words?

661
00:30:13,293 --> 00:30:18,575
Oh, let me just clarify, it is
not just me who likes Aga!

662
00:30:19,357 --> 00:30:22,580
The guy I possessed likes him, too!

663
00:30:22,605 --> 00:30:24,460
How did that happen? This is Chef K!

664
00:30:24,485 --> 00:30:27,301
Speaking English, but I
don’t even understand!

665
00:30:27,326 --> 00:30:28,326
Oh, oh! Tso K!

666
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:39,260
What happened?

667
00:30:39,393 --> 00:30:40,393
Huh?

668
00:30:40,777 --> 00:30:42,804
Oh! What happened?! Why is it like that?!

669
00:30:49,152 --> 00:30:51,705
Why is everyone here?
Why are they all staring at me?

670
00:30:51,765 --> 00:30:52,545
What happened?!

671
00:30:52,570 --> 00:30:53,771
They said we got possessed!

672
00:30:53,796 --> 00:30:55,974
- That’s true!
- You became a woman!

673
00:30:56,505 --> 00:30:57,539
Me, a foreigner?!

674
00:30:57,572 --> 00:30:59,018
- Yes!
- A foreigner!

675
00:30:59,043 --> 00:31:00,518
Wow, gross! Really?!

676
00:31:00,543 --> 00:31:01,422
Look, look!

677
00:31:01,447 --> 00:31:03,859
Hey! Why do I have—why do I have this?!

678
00:31:03,959 --> 00:31:05,579
I just told you!

679
00:31:10,228 --> 00:31:11,228
You’re back now?

680
00:31:11,526 --> 00:31:12,526
You’re back?!

681
00:31:13,298 --> 00:31:14,532
No, idiot, it’s cold!

682
00:31:16,035 --> 00:31:17,575
- One more, one more!
- It’s cold!

683
00:31:21,252 --> 00:31:24,998
Oh my gosh! I’m back!

684
00:31:35,201 --> 00:31:37,868
You guys are terrible! You are
actually sad about me coming back?!

685
00:31:37,893 --> 00:31:42,723
Ted, thank you so much
for saving our three friends!

686
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:44,097
Thank you so much!

687
00:31:44,170 --> 00:31:44,903
You’re welcome.

688
00:31:45,007 --> 00:31:46,900
Thank you, thank you, Ted Makipot!

689
00:31:47,219 --> 00:31:49,819
- Thank you so much!
- Thank you, thank you, thank you!

690
00:31:49,844 --> 00:31:52,032
Wait. Hold on.

691
00:31:53,342 --> 00:31:55,756
Uh, one, two, three…hey, why
are there only three of us here?

692
00:31:55,781 --> 00:31:58,014
Weren’t there four of us
playing spirit of the glass?

693
00:31:58,052 --> 00:31:59,607
- Where’s Chard?
- Yeah, where is he?

694
00:31:59,632 --> 00:32:00,147
Chard!

695
00:32:00,172 --> 00:32:01,989
- Chard!
- Where’s Chard?!

696
00:32:02,130 --> 00:32:03,816
Good afternoon! Good afternoon!

697
00:32:04,761 --> 00:32:06,128
Oh, what happened here?!

698
00:32:06,214 --> 00:32:06,867
A goblin?!

699
00:32:06,933 --> 00:32:10,888
- He looks like a rat, though.
- I just woke up. What’s going on?!

700
00:32:16,873 --> 00:32:19,480
Oh no, Chard! Who possessed you?!

701
00:32:19,505 --> 00:32:21,079
- No one possessed me!
- Tell us!

702
00:32:21,104 --> 00:32:22,191
- Who possessed you?!
- It’s me!

703
00:32:22,215 --> 00:32:23,964
- Who possessed you?!
- It’s me, it’s me!

704
00:32:23,989 --> 00:32:29,822
No, no! It’s still me!
Iskineport! Chard, Chard!

705
00:32:39,626 --> 00:32:40,800
Slowly, slowly.

706
00:32:40,825 --> 00:32:41,825
Slowly.

707
00:32:46,566 --> 00:32:47,566
There!

708
00:32:51,243 --> 00:32:52,783
There, okay.

709
00:32:53,871 --> 00:32:54,871
Grandpa Roman,

710
00:32:55,493 --> 00:33:00,837
we almost didn’t get to visit you, but
we’re happy that we’re all here now.

711
00:33:01,131 --> 00:33:08,262
That’s right, and Lolo Roman, please
continue to watch over and guide us.

712
00:33:09,293 --> 00:33:17,185
Roman, I’m sorry I kept avoiding
you when you possessed me.

713
00:33:17,759 --> 00:33:20,379
But now, I agree.

714
00:33:24,061 --> 00:33:28,266
Wait a minute, Lola Maxi.
What do you mean by “agree”?

715
00:33:28,673 --> 00:33:36,457
I mean, I agree that Roman can
possess you. I’ll step aside for you!

716
00:33:37,058 --> 00:33:42,552
Oh, I’m sorry, Lola Maxi, but I
don’t really go for people your age.

717
00:33:42,875 --> 00:33:47,300
To put it in Mahjong terms,
you’re kind of... discardable.

718
00:33:47,337 --> 00:33:51,664
Choo..you’re being choosy?!

719
00:33:51,998 --> 00:33:53,172
Fine, whatever.

720
00:33:53,197 --> 00:33:54,594
Chard, what about you?

721
00:33:54,619 --> 00:33:57,830
If Lola Maxi wants it, then... I’m here!

722
00:34:00,263 --> 00:34:03,276
I’m not that desperate! What a pain!

723
00:34:05,826 --> 00:34:07,353
But hey, it’s fine.

724
00:34:08,656 --> 00:34:12,976
Lolo Roman, thank you
so much for visiting us.

725
00:34:14,084 --> 00:34:15,084
Thank you, really.

726
00:34:15,694 --> 00:34:20,733
At least, you know, he
sees, he knows we’re aware.

727
00:34:20,817 --> 00:34:21,817
We’re guided.

728
00:34:22,045 --> 00:34:25,638
And wherever he is,
we haven’t forgotten him.

729
00:34:25,972 --> 00:34:26,673
That’s right.

730
00:34:26,698 --> 00:34:28,558
- That’s what matters most.
- Really, Dad?

731
00:34:28,668 --> 00:34:30,415
Yeah! Absolutely!

732
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:34,042
Because through problems and happiness...

733
00:34:34,742 --> 00:34:35,289
come here!

734
00:34:35,314 --> 00:34:39,092
Pers is first, Pers is the star!

735
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:40,394
Hey!

736
00:34:40,419 --> 00:34:41,419
Hey!

737
00:34:41,993 --> 00:34:42,993
What was that?

738
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:43,978
What was that?!

739
00:34:44,003 --> 00:34:44,950
Andres, you go look over there!

740
00:34:44,975 --> 00:34:46,043
You go check!

741
00:34:46,068 --> 00:34:48,543
- I’ll peek, but I’m not scared if…
- Maybe it’s…

742
00:34:48,609 --> 00:34:49,609
Lolo Roman?

743
00:34:52,739 --> 00:34:53,392
Ghost!

744
00:34:53,417 --> 00:34:54,417
Hey!

745
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:02,963
- Who’s that?!
- Who’s that?!

746
00:35:08,685 --> 00:35:10,185
It’s a prank!

747
00:35:11,496 --> 00:35:12,576
Tasha!

748
00:35:12,737 --> 00:35:14,857
Wait, that was way too much!

749
00:35:15,799 --> 00:35:17,972
What are you up to this time?

750
00:35:18,483 --> 00:35:20,356
Honestly, I have no idea either.

751
00:35:23,212 --> 00:35:25,105
We’ll have a mass baptism.

752
00:35:25,143 --> 00:35:26,423
Who’s going to be the godfather?

753
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:27,280
Kuya Aga…

754
00:35:27,305 --> 00:35:28,584
- Kuya Aga…
- Kuya Aga.

755
00:35:28,609 --> 00:35:30,453
Jennifer!

756
00:35:31,141 --> 00:35:32,528
- Jennifer?!
- Jennifer?!

757
00:35:32,553 --> 00:35:35,029
His real name is Jennifer!

758
00:35:35,144 --> 00:35:38,410
I need two tattoo artists to go to America!

759
00:35:38,435 --> 00:35:40,063
I’m not leaving Kuya Aga!

760
00:35:40,088 --> 00:35:41,818
It’s for a hundred thousand a month!

761
00:35:41,933 --> 00:35:43,513
- Hey!
- Ouch, ouch, ouch!

762
00:35:43,538 --> 00:35:44,220
Come on!

763
00:35:44,245 --> 00:35:44,944
Kuya Aga!

764
00:35:44,969 --> 00:35:45,642
How are you?

765
00:35:45,667 --> 00:35:47,198
Could you also be the
godfather of our child?

766
00:35:47,222 --> 00:35:48,321
When I have enough again…

767
00:35:48,409 --> 00:35:49,736
You’re so selective about who to help!

768
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,640
My name is now Iskineport!

769
00:35:51,665 --> 00:35:53,446
You can still make it to the mass baptism!

770
00:35:53,471 --> 00:35:55,331
It’s so hard to think of
what gift to give, isn’t it?

771
00:35:55,355 --> 00:35:56,457
Our money isn’t enough.

772
00:35:56,482 --> 00:35:57,482
I have an idea.

773
00:36:00,770 --> 00:36:03,490
Do you renounce Satan?

774
00:36:03,515 --> 00:36:05,447
Yes, we renounce him!

775
00:36:07,373 --> 00:36:08,613
Mmm, why is it always about me?
